  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The DxN Cytomegalovirus (CMV) assay is an in vitro diagnostic assay intended as an aid in the
      management of CMV-infected individuals undergoing antiviral therapy. the purpose of the study
      is to establish the clinical performance of the DxN CMV Assay for plasma samples in the
      intended use population.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
